<center><h1>Sigma Query Language</h1></center>

<IMG ALT=o SRC="fig7.gif" align=right>

<h2>To extract 3 time slices from a hypermapped virtual world R
the query in mathematical notation is:
<br> S<sub>t</sub>
(t<sub>1</sub>, t<sub>2</sub>, t<sub>3</sub>) R<br><br>

In SigmaQL language the query can be expressed as:</h2><b>
<pre>
SELECT     t
CLUSTER    t1, t2, t3
FROM       R</pre>
